ducing fuel consumption and other key operating costs our broad array of equipment and services support every type of railway operator from major national and international railway systems to short lines and highspeed urban transit networks   harsco corporation terms of use harsco metals  minerals rail industrial harsco corporation to release second quarter results and hold conference call harscos rail division receives multiunit uk stoneblower order harscos protran technology unit to outfit denvers entire regional railway fleet about us news  media investor relations careers safetysustainability contact nyse hsc   as of   pm     harsco has redefined our core values and launched a new business system unifying our global businesses around essential principles and processes learn about harsco’s business system and our core values harsco has redefined our core values and launched a new business system unifying our global businesses around essential principles and processes learn about harsco’s business system and our core values throughout  harsco continued to build on our long history of conscientious corporate citizenship see some of what weve been doing to affirm our commitments to our customers and communities in harscos firstever corporate responsibility summary  am  one of our core specialties is minimizing the environmental impacts of metal production by turning waste products into useful materials and helping create a greener world our steelphalt™ business leads the way in the use of steel slag for asphalt road construction click here for a short video in the natural gas industry efficiency and speed are essential to market success centerpoint harsco industrial airxchangers’ new manufacturing hub puts productivity at the center of our focus learn how harsco industrial airxchangers’ commitment to lean manufacturing is helping us meet customer demand   harsco corporation terms of use  privacy policy  uk modern slavery act   site map about us  news  media  investo