t and multiple shipping points ikg is your premier mezzanine source more info   mebac® the first family of slip resistance mebac® is available only from harsco industrial ikg ikg in five grades of slipresistant coating a valuable part of any slip and fall loss prevention program mebac® is durable and low maintenance apply it to your grating once and it provides slip resistance for years more info   harsco industrial ikg gratecoat® through a multimillion dollar investment in powder coat technology harsco industrial ikg ikg is the first grating manufacturer to offer powder coat finish as a standard paint for bar grating our new gratecoat® finish is available in standard colors of black and gray  or we can match the paint colors on your existing applications more info   specialty products as the industry leader in specialty products in both steel and aluminum harsco industrial ikg ikg offers a wide range of swaged safetgrid® pressure locked and heavy weld grating products manufactured to naamm standards and customized to your needs ikg has over  years’ experience in sales engineering project management and quality control which means fewer problems for you in the field more info   grateguard™ an innovative new approach to high security fencing our skilled sales personnel and engineering staff are highly knowledgably in the perimeter industry providing solutions to customers in a wide range of commercial applications discover how grateguard™ can fulfill your specific project needs more info more info       harsco industrial ikg all rights reserved privacy policy  terms of use  site map  back to top harsco industrial ikg is a registered trademark of harsco corporation a division of harsco corporation flashratings  principles facebook autocomplete demo post a rating  month price target   trending sign up log in flashratings principles  flashratings mission is to provide you  the investor  with as much honest and professional research on your investments as possible  we be